import pandas as pd

# Load the dataset
data_path = 'data/东方财富概念版块/水产养殖.csv'
df = pd.read_csv(data_path)

# Ensure 'trade_date' is in datetime format

# Extract year, month, and day from 'trade_date'
df['Year'] = df['trade_date'].dt.year
df['Month'] = df['trade_date'].dt.month

# Plot the trend of 'total_mv' over 'trade_date'

from matplotlib.font_manager import FontProperties

font_path = "/Library/Fonts/SimHei.ttf"

plt.rcParams['font.family'] = 'SimHei'

    ax.plot(data['trade_date'], data['total_mv'], label=filename)

ax.set_xlabel('Trade Date')
ax.set_ylabel('Total MV (万元)')
ax.set_title('水产养殖行业研究报告')
ax.legend(prop=font)

# Save the plot
output_path = '/Users/ash/Desktop/本科/毕业论文/writer/output/2025水产养殖行业研究报告/image'
fig.savefig(f'{output_path}/东方财富概念版块_水产养殖行业研究报告.png')
